[The measures that have been implemented as quickly as they have been are impressive and one hopes will succeed in stomping out this latest flare-up of Ebola. With virus persisting from the 2018-2020 Nord Kivu/Ituri EVD outbreak, it adds to the difficulty of ending an outbreak. When can one really feel certain an Ebola outbreak is over? - Mod.LK

